Look!

00:20:28.790 --> 00:20:31.160
Y-You startled me, okay?!

00:20:31.160 --> 00:20:34.040
You moron!

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:37.080
Moron?! You're insulting me now?
What gives, Ishikawa-kun?!

00:20:37.080 --> 00:20:38.700
You're not gonna listen otherwise!

00:20:38.700 --> 00:20:39.370
--The hell does that mean?!

00:20:39.370 --> 00:20:41.080
--It means--
--The hell does that mean?!

00:20:41.080 --> 00:20:42.290
Shit, sorry!

00:20:42.290 --> 00:20:44.200
That hurt.

00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:49.080
Yo, your eyes are scary!

00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:52.160
Miyamura! Time out, time out!

00:20:56.040 --> 00:20:58.200
It... It was self-defense!

00:20:58.200 --> 00:20:59.830
You beat the shit out of me!

00:20:59.830 --> 00:21:03.200
That was uncalled for <i>and</i>
has nothing to do with Hori!

00:21:04.200 --> 00:21:06.450
It was just 'cause I startled you, then?

00:21:06.450 --> 00:21:09.910
No, I was also kind of pissed at you.

00:21:09.910 --> 00:21:14.450
You're not supposed to admit that!
You're freakin' me out, man!

00:21:14.450 --> 00:21:18.450
I pushed Miyamura too far. It's my fault.

00:21:18.450 --> 00:21:21.410
I'm so sorry, Miyamura.

00:21:21.410 --> 00:21:24.660
C'mon, go apologize to him and make up.

00:21:27.290 --> 00:21:33.250
Wow, Miyamura said it was all his fault.

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:34.870
That's not what Toru said.

00:21:34.870 --> 00:21:37.870
First they beat each other up,
now they both take the blame?

00:21:37.870 --> 00:21:38.750
They're so weird.

00:21:38.750 --> 00:21:40.700
I know!

00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:44.450
Man, what were they even fighting about?

00:21:46.870 --> 00:21:50.700
We were fighting about Hori-san.

00:21:50.700 --> 00:21:52.540
Please don't tell anyone.

00:21:55.450 --> 00:21:58.370
What? What is it?

00:21:58.370 --> 00:22:02.000
It's so cool that guys can just
duke it out with each other.

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:03.910
Yeah, it sure is.

